title: Episode 334 “Rock The Bells”
itunes:title: Episode 334 “Rock The Bells”
description:
N.O.R.E. & DJ EFN are the Drink Champs. In this episode, we travelled to New York for LL Cool J’s “Rock The Bells” festival!! 

We chop it up with a variety of guests like Ice Cube, Onyx (Fredro Starr & Sticky Fingaz), Fat Joe, Peter Gunz, Cipha Sounds, Peter Rosenberg, Lance Un Rivera, Spliff Star & LL Cool J! 

Lots of great stories that you don’t want to miss!!

Make some noise!!! 💐💐💐🏆🏆🏆

Listen and subscribe at https://www.drinkchamps.com
